(87, 1, NULL, 'Comprehensive automatic control', 'التحكم الآلي الشامل', NULL, '<p class=\"ql-align-center\"><strong>Classic control</strong></p><ol><li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Introduction To Control System</li><li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Type Of Electrical Key</li><li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Push Buttons Relay Latch Relay Solid State Relay</li><li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Theory Of Relay Action NC NO</li><li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Design Control Diagram For&nbsp;Control System </li><li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;How To Fine NC NO &nbsp;From Relay Diagram Ant Timer And Manual&nbsp;</li><li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Electrical Interlock Mechanical Interlock</li><li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Different&nbsp;Between Contactor And Relay</li><li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Different&nbsp;Between Relay&nbsp;And SSR</li><li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Different Between Timers </li><li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;motor control Start stop &nbsp;Star delta&nbsp;FWD BWD </li><li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Project&nbsp;Temperature Controller Using&nbsp;AC&nbsp;Contactor&nbsp;</li><li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Project&nbsp;Temperature Controller Using&nbsp;SSR</li><li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Project&nbsp;Temperature Controller&nbsp;Using Relay&nbsp;AC&nbsp;Contactor</li></ol><p>Basic PLC</p><p>1-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Introduction To PLC System </p><p>2-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Differences Type Of &nbsp;PLC</p><p>3-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;PLC Structure</p><p>4-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;PLC Selection</p><p>5-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Input Output Device</p><p>6-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Ladder And PLC Program</p><p>7-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Delta PLC Programming And Environments (WPLSOFT &amp; ISPSOFR)</p><p>8-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Delta PLC Digital Programming&nbsp;</p><p>9-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Timers And Counters &nbsp;&nbsp;auxiliary &nbsp;Relay</p><p>Advance PLC &amp; Automation </p><p>1-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Introduction&nbsp;To Automation System</p><p>2-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Extensions modules programming</p><p>3-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Analog input programming (4-20mA)</p><p>4-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Analog output programming (0-10V)</p><p>5-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;LVDT sensor programming</p><p>6-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Wiring of sensor and&nbsp;programming</p><p>7-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Temperature control and thermocouple programming </p><p>8-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;HMI programming (DOP SOFT)</p><p>9-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;DELTA TP Editor control and programming </p><p>10-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Data memory and registers programming </p><p>11-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Motor control&nbsp;VFD&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p><br></p>', '<p>-</p>', 3, 130, '28775.560', '_1677756381917.webp', '[]', '[]', 1, 0, 'd004d3243e4ee05b48da80eefd57fff2', 1, NULL, '[]', '[]', '-', '-', '-', '-', '[]', '_1677756381918.jpg', '', '2023-03-02 11:26:21', '2025-05-18 09:00:18'),
